    "This proves advantageous, especially in the context of intent management and resilience (see Section III-B and III-C).",
    "Apart from the continual learning capability, RAG with evolving knowledge enables the retrieved knowledge from either a textbook or the standard also to be dynamically adjusted to cater to the specific application demands.",
